<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   When Amy Irving isn't working in a movie, she
gets together with other performers for play readings in Hollywood,
the actress told ``Parade'' magazine for its Oct. 30 issue.
   ``People like Ed Asner, John Lithgow, Marsha Mason and Ted
Danson'' join her at the Thursday night sessions, said Irving, wife
